Scenario 1: Server Not Reachable
Check:
ping server-ip

Verify Network:
ip addr

Check Firewall:
sudo ufw status

Scenario 2: Jenkins Not Starting
Check Service:
systemctl status jenkins

View Logs:
journalctl -xeu jenkins

Verify Port:
ss -tulpn | grep 8080

Scenario 3: Disk Full
Check:
df -h

Largest Directories:
du -sh /*

Find Large Files:
find / -type f -size +500M

Scenario 4: High CPU Usage
Identify Process:
top

Kill Process:
kill -9 PID

Scenario 5: Website Down
Check Service:
systemctl status nginx

Check Port:
ss -tulpn | grep 80

Check Logs:
tail -f /var/log/nginx/error.log

DevOps Production Troubleshooting Flow
User Reports Issue
        ↓
Check Service Status
        ↓
Check Logs
        ↓
Check CPU / Memory
        ↓
Check Network
        ↓
Check Disk Space
        ↓
Identify Root Cause
        ↓
Fix Issue
        ↓
Validate Service
        ↓
Close Incident
